## Components

### Applications

- **Repo:** [ohid-aihc-frontend](https://github.com/ukhsa-collaboration/ohid-aihc-frontend/)
- React frontend used to interact with the API

- **Repo:** [ohid-aihc](https://github.com/ukhsa-collaboration/ohid-aihc)
- FastAPI-based application that uses Amazon Bedrock for LLMs and PostgreSQL for data storage

### Infrastructure as Code (IaC)

- **Repo:** [ohid-aihc-iac](https://github.com/ukhsa-collaboration/ohid-aihc-iac)
- Terraform code defining AWS infrastructure for all environments.

